        },
        "rich_text_8DL9Df": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1st Para",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Engagement rings have always been more than just symbols of love—they are statements of personal style, values, and individuality. If you are asking “what are engagement ring trends” in 2025, the answer is both exciting and diverse. This year, couples are looking beyond classic solitaires to rings that reflect their modern lifestyle, ethical choices, and aesthetic preferences. From swirling shapes to bold men’s bands, lab-grown diamonds to colored gemstones, the 2025 trends show that engagement rings are evolving with the times.</p><p>The new trends are designed for couples who want more than a beautiful ring—they want a piece that tells their story. Whether it is elegance, sustainability, or personalization, understanding what are engagement ring trends will help you make a choice that combines tradition with innovation, beauty with meaning, and fashion with timeless symbolism.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bUfHBT": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "1.  Swirling Shape Engagement Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>1.  Swirling Shape Engagement Rings</h2><p>One of the most captivating answers to “what are engagement ring trends” in 2025 is the rise of swirling, fluid bands. Unlike traditional straight bands, these designs feature intertwined curves that symbolize eternal love and connection. The soft, flowing lines give the ring a romantic, ethereal feel, making it highly popular among couples who want their ring to reflect both elegance and individuality.</p>",
            "custom_id": "swirling"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_gEUkmH": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Swirling_Shape_Engagement_Rings.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Why swirling shapes are trending:</p><ul><li>Represent love and unity in a visually dynamic way</li><li>Ideal for couples who want something unique and artistic</li><li>Offer flexibility for stacking or pairing with other jewelry</li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_mQyMzj": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Fashion tip: These rings are versatile—they look stunning with minimalist outfits for work or casual events and shine beautifully with evening gowns for special occasions. Swirling shapes also pair well with lab-grown diamonds, offering eco-friendly luxury that doesn’t compromise style.</p><p>Swirling rings answer the question of what are engagement ring trends for couples who value romantic symbolism with modern design.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_JmwFBb": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "2.  East-West Engagement Ring Settings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>2.  East-West Engagement Ring Settings</h2><p>Another exciting answer to “what are engagement ring trends” is the East-West diamond setting, where the diamond is mounted horizontally rather than vertically. This design adds a modern twist to classic stones, giving the ring a sleek and contemporary appeal. Oval, marquise, and emerald cuts work particularly well with East-West settings, creating a dramatic and stylish silhouette.</p>",
            "custom_id": "eastwest"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_9aMr3D": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/East-West_Engagement_Ring_Settings.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Why East-West settings are trending:</p><ul><li>Provides a modern minimalist aesthetic<br/><br/></li><li>Perfect for couples who want to stand out without being extravagant<br/><br/></li><li>Complements both casual and formal wear effortlessly</li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_8DUXP6": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Fashion tip: East-West rings pair beautifully with subtle metallic jewelry or monochromatic outfits, allowing the ring to take center stage. By incorporating this design, couples can explore what are engagement ring trends while embracing unique creativity and sophistication.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_Jc4E4r": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "3. Bold Men’s Engagement Bands",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>3. Bold Men’s Engagement Bands</h2><p>A growing trend in 2025, answering what are engagement ring trends, is bold men’s engagement bands. Traditionally, engagement rings have been associated with women, but modern couples are opting for chunky gold or platinum bands for men, combining masculine elegance with modern style.</p>",
            "custom_id": "bold"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_TG38Ca": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Bold_Men_s_Engagement_Bands.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Why bold men’s bands are trending:</p><ul><li>They represent strength and individuality<br/></li><li>Allow men to actively participate in the engagement ritual<br/></li><li>Offer durability and comfort for everyday wear</li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_DhV8Bc": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Fashion tip: Pair bold bands with smart casual or tailored outfits to make a subtle yet stylish statement. These rings prove that what are engagement ring trends isn’t limited to women—it’s about celebrating both partners equally.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_bbpdxU": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "4. Pave & Halo Sparkle Engagement Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>4. Pave & Halo Sparkle Engagement Rings</h2><p>For those asking “what are engagement ring trends”, pave and halo styles remain a top choice. These rings feature tiny diamonds encircling the main stone, creating maximum sparkle and a sense of luxury without being overbearing.</p>",
            "custom_id": "pave"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_G3MmrD": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Pave_Halo_Sparkle_Engagement_Rings.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Why pave and halo rings are trending:</p><ul><li>Enhance the central stone’s brilliance and size<br/><br/></li><li>Perfect for evening events, weddings, and special occasions<br/><br/></li><li>Combine modern design with vintage-inspired glamour</li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_qwtz9D": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Fashion tip: Pair pave and halo rings with delicate necklaces and studs to balance elegance and shimmer. These rings are a clear example of what are engagement ring trends, blending timeless beauty with contemporary luxury.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_6xgWz3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "5. Vintage Inspired Engagement Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>5. Vintage Inspired Engagement Rings</h2><p>Vintage-inspired designs are making a significant comeback in 2025. Couples seeking what are engagement ring trends are drawn to art deco, retro, and antique-inspired rings, which combine modern craftsmanship with nostalgic charm.</p>",
            "custom_id": "vintage"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_AWtNat": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "name": "5.",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Vintage_Inspired_Engagement_Rings.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Why vintage rings are trending:</p><ul><li>Offer timeless elegance and artistic detail<br/><br/></li><li>Appeal to romantics and collectors alike<br/><br/></li><li>Work perfectly as statement pieces or heirloom-style jewelry<br/></li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_AexEgM": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Fashion tip: Vintage rings complement both modern bridal gowns and classic formal wear, creating a striking contrast that highlights intricate detailing. For couples exploring what are engagement ring trends, vintage designs provide soulful beauty with historical significance.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_xii4nX": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "6. Lab-Grown Diamonds: Ethical & Affordable Luxury",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>6. Lab-Grown Diamonds: Ethical & Affordable Luxury</h2><p>Ethical luxury is at the forefront of 2025 engagement ring trends. Couples asking what are engagement ring trends are increasingly choosing lab-grown diamonds, which offer the same brilliance as mined diamonds but are eco-friendly and cost-effective.</p>",
            "custom_id": "labgrown"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_JDQbJG": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Lab_Grown_Diamonds_Ethical_Affordable_Luxury.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Benefits of lab-grown diamonds:</p><ul><li>Environmentally sustainable<br/></li><li>Affordable, allowing for larger or higher-quality stones<br/></li><li>Ethically sourced with no compromise on quality</li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_3Y7JpP": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Fashion tip: Lab-grown diamonds pair beautifully with customized rings and modern designs, allowing couples to choose a ring that is both stunning and sustainable. This trend shows that what are engagement ring trends now includes conscious luxury for the modern couple.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_fN3RJE": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "7. ",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>7. Toi et Moi Rings: The “You and I” Statement</h2><p>Toi et Moi rings, featuring two stones side by side, are another highlight of 2025 engagement rings. This design symbolizes the union of two souls and offers a meaningful alternative to single-stone rings.</p>",
            "custom_id": "toi"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_YQcqz7": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/oi_et_Moi_Rings_The_You_and_I_Statement.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Why Toi et Moi rings are trending:</p><ul><li>Represent balance, partnership, and individuality<br/></li><li>Offer flexibility in choosing stone colors and shapes<br/></li><li>Popular among celebrity couples for their statement-making elegance</li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_n44UUw": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Fashion tip: Pair these rings with simple bands or delicate rings to keep the focus on the dual-stone design. They are a perfect example of what are engagement ring trends, combining romantic symbolism with contemporary design.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_rQKzCe": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "8",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>8. Stacking Rings & Personalization</h2><p>Stacked and personalized rings are a favorite among younger generations. Couples exploring what are engagement ring trends are choosing rings that evolve with their love story, allowing for mix-and-match designs, gemstone additions, and meaningful engravings.</p>",
            "custom_id": "stacking"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_wJtpft": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Stacking_Rings_Personalization.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Why stacking rings are trending:</p><ul><li>Endless styling possibilities and personalization<br/></li><li>Reflects personal stories and milestones<br/></li><li>Works with minimalist and ornate designs alike.</li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_DwezPq": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Fashion tip: Stack thin gold or platinum bands for a chic layered look that complements everyday outfits and formal events. Stacking rings are a creative way to embrace what are engagement ring trends while making each ring uniquely personal.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_RCeb77": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "9. Oval-Cut & Unique Shapes Engagement Rings",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>9. Oval-Cut & Unique Shapes Engagement Rings</h2><p>While round solitaires remain classic, 2025 sees a shift toward oval, pear, marquise, and other unique shapes. These cuts enhance the visual size of the stone and symbolize infinity and elegance, appealing to modern couples asking what are engagement ring trends.</p>",
            "custom_id": "oval"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_PeMxMx": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Oval-Cut_Unique_Shapes_Engagement_Rings.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Why unique shapes are trending:</p><ul><li>Look larger than their carat size<br/><br/></li><li>Offer distinctive elegance for non-traditional brides<br/><br/></li><li>Complement pave, halo, and solitaire settings<br/></li></ul>",
            "reverse_layout": false,
            "custom_id": "",
            "image_size_option": "medium"
          }
        },
        "rich_text_aTEwB3": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Fashion tip: Pair unique shapes with minimalist jewelry to ensure the ring remains the centerpiece. Oval and unconventional cuts highlight what are engagement ring trends by combining style, symbolism, and sophistication.</p>",
            "custom_id": ""
          }
        },
        "rich_text_ADDTPa": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Buying Guide: Smart Tips for Hallmarked Jewellery",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>10. Colored Gemstones Engagement Ring</h2><p>Colored gemstones are gaining momentum in 2025. Couples exploring what are engagement ring trends are selecting sapphires, rubies, and colored diamonds for personalized vibrancy and emotional significance.</p>",
            "custom_id": "gemstone"
          }
        },
        "image_with_text_aryLe4": {
          "type": "image_with_text",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/Colored_Gemstones_Engagement_Ring.jpg",
            "text": "<p>Popular gemstone colors and meanings:</p><ul><li>Pink Sapphire: Love and romance<br/><br/></li><li>Blue Sapphire: Loyalty and calm<br/><br/></li><li>Yellow Diamond: Happiness and warmth<br/><br/></li><li>Ruby: Passion and vitality</li></ul>",
