        "rich_text_CNg3En": {
          "type": "rich_text",
          "name": "Conclusion",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<h2>Conclusion </h2><p>When asking “what are engagement ring trends in 2025,” the answer is clear: rings that balance tradition, innovation, individuality, and sustainability. From swirling shapes to bold men’s bands, lab-grown diamonds to vibrant colored gemstones, the trends offer something for every couple. The ideal engagement ring should reflect your story, style, and values, making your choice both meaningful and fashionable.</p>",
